Author: Little-Rexy
Text: You struggles are real. I can suggest that you keep talking about what is at the core of your feelings and attitude towards food, it can only help you.

Author: portraitofalady87
Text: There is heaps to unpack here. Im going to focus on one thing. You heard of imposter syndrome? It comes hand in hand with the kinds of thought patterns linked to anorexia. Youre not a fake, and you are struggling right now. Your post says that you dont want to get sick, but you already seem to be. Did you notice that conflict? I always struggled with identifying my triggers, and when I was and wasnt well.. like I could just say "im not going to be sick today" and bam my ed was gone.
